        <updateDate>2021-06-15T19:19:43Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Honor and Remember Flag Recognition Act</b></p> <p>This bill designates the Honor and Remember Flag, created by Honor and Remember, Inc., as a national symbol to honor service members who died in the line of duty and specifies federal locations and dates for its display.</p>]]></text>
